{"@context":"http://iiif.io/api/presentation/3/context.json","id":"https://digbmc.github.io/pta-manifests/phan/phan-13604/manifest.json","type":"Manifest","label":{"none":["PHAN-13604"]},"metadata":[{"label":{"none":["Timestamp"]},"value":{"none":["1:36:04"]}},{"label":{"none":["Film"]},"value":{"none":["Phantom Thread"]}},{"label":{"none":["Distance"]},"value":{"none":["full shot"]}},{"label":{"none":["Angle"]},"value":{"none":["low"]}},{"label":{"none":["Location"]},"value":{"none":["interior"]}},{"label":{"none":["Movement"]},"value":{"none":["mobile, tracking"]}},{"label":{"none":["Composition"]},"value":{"none":["two shot"]}}],"summary":{"none":["A man and woman sit eating breakfast on a balcony in Switzerland."]},"thumbnail":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-13604/tiles/full/300,169/0/default.jpg","type":"Image","format":"image/jpeg","height":169,"width":300}],"homepage":[{"id":"PHAN-13604","type":"Text","format":"text/html","label":{"none":["Object homepage"]}}],"items":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-13604/canvas/1","type":"Canvas","height":1080,"width":1920,"label":{"none":["PHAN-13604"]},"thumbnail":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-13604/tiles/full/300,169/0/default.jpg","type":"Image","format":"image/jpeg","height":169,"width":300}],"items":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-13604/canvas/1/annopage-1","type":"AnnotationPage","items":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-13604/canvas/1/annopage-1/anno-1","type":"Annotation","motivation":"painting","target":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-13604/canvas/1","body":{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-13604/tiles/full/1920,1080/0/default.jpg","type":"Image","format":"image/jpeg","height":1080,"width":1920,"service":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-13604/tiles","type":"ImageService3","profile":"http://iiif.io/api/image/3/level0.json"}]}}]}],"annotations":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-13604/canvas/1/page/p1","type":"AnnotationPage","items":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-13604/canvas/1/cc8eda75-074b-4406-b0ca-acf82709870b","type":"Annotation","motivation":"commenting","body":[{"created":"2026-07-01T13:41:45.962Z","creator":"lucia","purpose":"commenting","type":"TextualBody","format":"text/html","value":"<p>The camera continues to push in on Reynolds and Alma, already having done so during the proposal, the wedding, and the celebratory dinner. This camera movement suggests that the two are becoming even more closer and intimate. However, once Alma eats her breakfast loudly, it stops.&nbsp;</p>"}],"target":{"type":"SpecificResource","source":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-13604/canvas/1","selector":{"type":"FragmentSelector","conformsTo":"http://www.w3.org/TR/media-frags/","value":"xywh=pixel:531.4285714285713,289.87012987012986,762.8571428571431,571.1688311688313"}}},{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-13604/canvas/1/6818e7ca-9ea0-48e7-8ae4-b99e5549956a","type":"Annotation","motivation":"commenting","body":[{"created":"2026-07-01T13:42:23.896Z","creator":"lucia","purpose":"commenting","type":"TextualBody","format":"text/html","value":"<p>This shot was filmed at the&nbsp; <a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" class=\"Hyperlink SCXW173712797 BCX2\" href=\"https://giessbach.ch/en\"><u>Grandhotel Giessbach</u></a> in Brienz, Switzerland. Lake Brienz can be seen in the background.&nbsp;</p>"}],"target":{"type":"SpecificResource","source":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-13604/canvas/1","selector":{"type":"FragmentSelector","conformsTo":"http://www.w3.org/TR/media-frags/","value":"xywh=pixel:349.090909090909,115.32467532467523,1088.5714285714287,429.3506493506495"}}},{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-13604/canvas/1/8aae8e7c-530f-483a-bd43-773c20e1d3f4","type":"Annotation","motivation":"commenting","body":[{"created":"2026-07-01T13:42:40.745Z","creator":"lucia","purpose":"commenting","type":"TextualBody","format":"text/html","value":"<p>Critic Ty Burr has compared this shot to a famous photograph of Russian writer Vladimir Nabokov and his wife, Vera, on the balcony of their balcony in the hotel in Montreux, Switzerland that they made their home after the success of <em>Lolita</em> (1955) (Burr, “<a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" class=\"Hyperlink SCXW223804625 BCX2\" href=\"https://tyburrswatchlist.substack.com/p/classics-of-the-new-millennium-phantom\"><u>Classics of the New Millennium</u></a>”). He aptly suggests that the film’s themes of power dynamics and twisted love recall Nabokov’s work.&nbsp;</p>"}],"target":{"type":"SpecificResource","source":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-13604/canvas/1","selector":{"type":"FragmentSelector","conformsTo":"http://www.w3.org/TR/media-frags/","value":"xywh=pixel:35.06493506493495,132.46753246753235,278.961038961039,125.4545454545455"}}}]}]}]}